parameters.name: name
parameters.description: A name of coordinator without -Coordinator suffix

parameters.name: controllers
parameters.description: A space-separated list of view controllers without -ViewController suffix

parameters.name: components
parameters.description: A space-separated list of entitines that needs to be tested and that are not related to particular view coordinator. It can be managers, services, ... Please use protocol reference like APIServicing instead of APIService where applicable.
